OL,3,CMP says government 'neglecting'
OL,4,Ccommunities in call for miners pension
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FA North East MP has called on the
OL,8,Fgovernment to reform mineworkers'
OL,9,Fpensions, accusing the government of
OL,10,F"widening economic inequality".
OL,12,FGrahame Morris, Labour MP for
OL,13,FEasington, said coalfield communities
OL,14,Fhad been neglected - with some retired
OL,15,Fminers receiving just #10 a month
OL,16,Funder the current pension scheme.
