OL,7,FSince it was privatised in 1994, half
OL,8,Fof surpluses from the Mineworkers'
OL,9,FPension Scheme have been paid to
OL,10,FGovernment amounting to a total of
OL,11,Faround #4.8 billion.
OL,13,FThe Easington MP told the Commons:
OL,14,F"The Government have ignored and
OL,15,Fneglected our most deprived mining
OL,16,Fcommunities, far from levelling-up,
OL,17,FConservative ministers have widened
OL,18,Feconomic inequality.
