OL,4,Ccommunities in call for miners pension
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,F"Low wealth in our region coincides
OL,8,Fwith low wages, making my region in
OL,9,Fthe North East the lowest paid region
OL,10,Fin the country.
OL,12,F"The Government could alleviate this
OL,13,Fin part by addressing past injustices
OL,14,Fand ensuring retirement security for
OL,15,Fmine workers and their widows, by
OL,16,Freforming the Mineworkers' Pension
OL,17,FScheme, in line with the (Business,
OL,18,FEnergy and Industrial Strategy) select
OL,19,Fcommittee recommendations that were
OL,20,Fpublished in April 2021.
