OL,7,F"My father died in the belief that his
OL,8,Fpit pension would provide security for
OL,9,Fmy aging mother ` who is incidentally
OL,10,Fcelebrating her 88th birthday on
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,F"However, we do know that some
OL,14,Fpensioners receive as little as #10 a
OL,15,Fweek from the Mineworkers' Pension
OL,16,FScheme. Our miners created the wealth
OL,17,Fthat made this country great, with the
OL,18,FMineworkers' Pension Scheme being
OL,19,Famongst the UK's largest pension funds.
