OL,7,F"However money that should be used to
OL,8,Fprovide security in retirement is
OL,9,Fbeing siphoned off by the Treasury,
OL,10,Ftaking half of all the pension funds'
OL,11,Fservices."
OL,13,FLabour MP for Wansbeck Ian Lavery,
OL,14,Fhimself a former miner, says he
OL,15,Fbelieves he is the only MP that is
OL,16,Fcurrently a member of the Mineworkers'
OL,17,FPension Scheme.
